      "para_id": "Q001066.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(Side 1, iii 1') .... He defeated .... He defeated Uruk . He defeated Urim . ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001066.9",
      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(Side 1, iv 1) The personal god of E-ana-tum , the builder of Ĝatumdug's temple , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001066.13",
      "line_range": "13",
      "translation": "(Side 1, iv 5) E-ana-tum fashioned ( the statue of ) Nanše . ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001066.17",
      "line_range": "17",
      "translation": "(Side 1, v 1) When ..., he assigned regular offerings to the lofty high temple for Nanše ; he assigned regular offerings to ... for Ninĝirsu , he assigned regular offerings to Nibru for Enlil . ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001066.31",
      "line_range": "31",
      "translation": "(Side 4, i 1') He brought ( this mortar ) before Nanše in the E-mah ."
    }
  ],
